OL,3,CSpygate 2.0? Saints accused of spying
OL,4,Con Play-off opponents
OL,6,FSouthampton Football Club have found
OL,7,Fthemselves at the centre of a scandal
OL,8,Fwhich has been dubbed Spygate 2.0.
OL,10,FThis weekend they play Middlesbrough
OL,11,Fin the first leg of their Play-off
OL,12,FSemi Final. Yesterday Middlesbriough
OL,13,Fmade a complaint to the English
OL,14,FFootball League (EFL) saying a Saints
OL,15,Fstaff member was spying on their
OL,16,Ftraining session.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
