OL,3,CSpygate 2.0? Saints accused of spying
OL,4,Con Play-off opponents
OL,6,FIt's alleged Southampton FC's
OL,7,Fperformance analyst was caught
OL,8,Frecording Boro training and taking
OL,9,Fpictures of tactics late on Thursday
OL,10,Fmorning. The reports say he was
OL,11,Fcaught, told to delete the footage and
OL,12,Fleave the area.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
