OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778351322
OL,3,CSpygate 2.0? Saints accused of spying
OL,4,Con Play-off opponents
OL,6,FMiddlesbrough then contacted the EFL
OL,7,Fto complain. In response the English
OL,8,FFootball League has issued a
OL,9,Fstatement: "The alleged incident is
OL,10,Fsaid to have taken place on
OL,11,FMiddlesbrough's private property by an
OL,12,Findividual identified to be associated
OL,13,Fwith Southampton. The League is
OL,14,Ftreating this matter as potential
OL,15,Fmisconduct under EFL regulations and
OL,16,Fwill be making no further comment at
OL,17,Fthis time."
OL,19,FAt this stage Southampton FC have not
OL,20,Fcommented.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
