OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778351322
OL,3,CSpygate 2.0? Saints accused of spying
OL,4,Con Play-off opponents
OL,6,FIt's been dubbed Spygate 2.0 as it
OL,7,Ffollows similar allegations in 2019
OL,8,Fwhen a member of Leeds' staff was
OL,9,Ffound acting suspiciously outside
OL,10,FDerby's training ground. Boss Marcelo
OL,11,FBielsa later revealed he'd sent a
OL,12,Fmember of staff to watch training
OL,13,Fsessions of every team Leeds played
OL,14,Fthat season. The EFL found Leeds
OL,15,Fbreached rules over treating teams
OL,16,Fwith "good faith". Leeds were fined
OL,17,F#200,000. A rule was then introduced -
OL,18,Fforbidding watching or filming
OL,19,Fopposition training up to 72 hours
OL,20,Fbefore a game.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
