PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1778351322
OL,3,CSpygate 2.0? Saints accused of spying
OL,4,Con Play-off opponents
OL,6,FIf charged, the matter will be handled
OL,7,Fby the EFL's disciplinary commission.
OL,8,FThis is an independent panel appointed
OL,9,Fthrough independent bodies to ensure
OL,10,Fneutrality. If Southampton FC are
OL,11,Ffound in breach of misconduct, the
OL,12,Fdisciplinary commission will have the
OL,13,Fpower to hand out whatever punishment
OL,14,Fthey see fit. The EFL's handbook lists
OL,15,Fpunishments such as points deductions,
OL,16,Ffines and transfer embargoes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
